│ ### Create a new file:                                                                                                                                                                   │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                  │
│ cat <<'EOF' > newfile.py                                                                                                                                                                 │
│ import numpy as np                                                                                                                                                                       │
